\begin{center}
{\Large \underline{\bf CERTIFICATE}}
\end{center}
\vspace{.3cm}
\noindent
This is to certify that the thesis entitled {\bf SEARCH FOR SUPERSEMMETRY, LEPTOQUARKS AND STUDY OF ADVANCED PILEUP MITIGATION TECHNIQUES WITH COMPACT MUON SOLENOID }, being submitted by {\bf Bibhuprasad Mahakud} for the award of the degree of {\bf Doctor of Philosophy} in Physics of Tata Institute of Fundamental Research, Mumbai is a record of bonafide research work carried out by him. He has carried out this investigation for last five years on the subject matter of the thesis under my supervision and I consider it worthy of consideration for the award of the degree of Doctor of Philosophy of the University. The works embodied in this thesis have not been submitted to any other university or institution for any degree or diploma.


